<typeStatus box="[1297,1345,837,861]" pageId="37" pageNumber="338">type</typeStatus>
locality is much drier than the cloud forests at 
<taxonomicName box="[604,723,871,896]" class="Insecta" family="Sphaeroceridae" genus="Boreantrops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="37" pageNumber="353" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="wayqecha">Wayqecha</taxonomicName>
, which may indicate a difference in habitat preference in this species.
</paragraph>
